        "subject": "LU-4578 ptlrpc: Adjust client rq_deadline for early reply",
        "message": "LU-4578 ptlrpc: Adjust client rq_deadline for early reply\n\nWhen it sends an early reply the server now offsets the request\narrival time to set the new deadline. We should adjust the client\nside, ptlrpc_at_recv_early_reply, accordingly.\n\nSigned-off-by: Chris Horn <hornc@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I2f8661ceba483e17ac2cb6e70f33b6fbe344ec24\n"
